WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:13.120 --> 00:01:14.650
No one followed you, right?

00:01:16.120 --> 00:01:16.850
What's wrong

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:17.800
with you?

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:19.280
I'm fine.

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:20.289
Listen to me.

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:22.520
Xu Xing found out about us.

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:23.580
He wants to kill me.

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:24.280
Kill you?

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:29.960
Someone

00:01:30.520 --> 00:01:32.180
used Li Xiaoru to kill Lin Ran,

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:34.360
then forced me to kill Li Xiaoru,

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:36.220
and now has sent Xu Xing to kill me.

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:40.460
I just realized it now.

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:44.410
He's forcing the four of us to kill each other.

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:46.050
What are you talking about?

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:47.380
Who is that person?

00:01:48.039 --> 00:01:48.970
I'm not sure yet.

00:01:49.960 --> 00:01:50.720
I just feel

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:52.979
it might be my college classmate.

00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:55.479
I'll explain it to you later.

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:56.640
The most important thing right now is

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:58.170
that Xu Xing might kill you.

00:01:58.680 --> 00:01:59.960
Even if he doesn't do it,

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:01.020
he will divorce you

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:03.860
and find a way to make you leave with nothing.

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:07.740
Before Xu Xing makes a move on you,

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.160
we need to come up with a plan.

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:13.410
Don't worry.

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:19.240
In this card game,

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:21.280
the order

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:22.720
and method of their deaths

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:24.050
match the case exactly.

00:02:28.760 --> 00:02:29.560
A week ago,

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:33.090
the four of them agreed to play a murder mystery game.

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:34.180
After that,

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:36.600
Li Xiaoru went to Lin Ran's house

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:37.840
and killed him.

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:44.880
I'm out,

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:46.810
falling to my death.

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:51.160
Then,

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:54.800
Li Xiaoru received a mysterious text message.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:56.300
Foreshadowing her death.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:57.520
I'm out.

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:04.640
Drowned.

00:03:08.480 --> 00:03:11.480
According to the next development of the game script,

00:03:12.680 --> 00:03:14.480
if nothing unexpected happens,

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:15.160
then

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.840
I should be tortured and killed now.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.600
Tortured and killed.

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:34.690
You lost.

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:41.880
No.

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:44.800
At the beginning of the game,

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.880
I gave you the witch's poison.

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:50.770
But you don't seem to have looked for an antidote.

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:53.420
So you should also issue a death card.

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:05.320
Poisoning.

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:09.520
We all lost.

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:23.680
The true core of this game

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:26.600
is to find the possessed monster.

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:28.880
But when we were playing,

00:04:29.760 --> 00:04:31.640
we all seemed to ignore this.

00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:37.400
So the real winner of this round is him,

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:41.930
the mysterious person who sent the texts.

00:04:43.760 --> 00:04:44.820
Elaborate on that.

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:46.480
I guess

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:51.920
this killer might not necessarily kill in person.

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:53.159
But

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:56.220
he must know these four people very well.

00:04:56.840 --> 00:04:59.280
Wants to use the chaotic relationships between the four of them

00:04:59.280 --> 00:05:00.880
to make them kill each other,

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:02.530
and then reap the benefits.

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:11.440
Lin Ran died from a fall.

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:12.880
Li Xiaoru drowned.

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:16.520
But Zhao Wenbing didn't.

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:17.840
He is currently

00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:19.000
on the run.

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:28.160
Hello?

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:31.280
Oh.

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:33.250
Oh, okay.

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:34.080
Yeah.

00:05:36.200 --> 00:05:37.000
What's wrong?

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:40.320
The cybersecurity colleagues just found out

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:42.200
that when Zhao Wenbing was escaping,

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:43.840
he received a mysterious phone call

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:45.040
telling Zhao Wenbing

00:05:45.400 --> 00:05:46.800
to change cars to escape.

00:05:51.880 --> 00:05:53.140
Then that makes sense.

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:55.290
That monster

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:58.520
wants to torture Zhao Wenbing a little longer.

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:00.480
Wants to let Xu Xing

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:03.080
fight with him a bit more.

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:08.780
Did Xu Xing want to kill Zhao Wenbing?

00:06:11.760 --> 00:06:13.690
We need to have a good talk with him.

00:06:19.200 --> 00:06:19.800
Officers,

00:06:20.280 --> 00:06:21.760
I've told you everything.

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:24.000
Instead of investigating the killer,

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.600
you come harass me every day.

00:06:25.880 --> 00:06:27.940
Be careful, I'll complain about you.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:30.480
Zhao Wenbing had a car accident.

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:32.610
Someone tampered with his car.

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:34.159
Does it have nothing to do with you?

00:06:34.159 --> 00:06:35.820
What does it have to do with me?

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:37.000
He's the legal director of my company.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.400
Do you think I'd kill him?

00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:41.200
There's one thing I want to tell you.

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:43.960
Before the accident of those three,

00:06:43.960 --> 00:06:45.820
they all received a text message.

00:06:46.080 --> 00:06:47.810
The content of the text message

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:51.260
was the advertisement for the LARP game you played.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:53.680
That's your business.

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:55.080
It has nothing to do with me.

00:06:55.080 --> 00:06:55.600
Indeed.

00:06:56.640 --> 00:06:57.920
Then I was wondering,

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:01.420
the next person to receive the text message,

00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:02.580
could it be you?

00:07:06.280 --> 00:07:07.920
I have dozens of bodyguards.

00:07:07.920 --> 00:07:08.800
Even if the King of Hell comes,

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:09.840
I can twist his head off.

00:07:09.840 --> 00:07:10.840
Do you believe it?

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:12.010
I believe it.

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:26.760
Hey.

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:29.530
Your action figure looks nice.

00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:31.040
Did I say you could touch my stuff?

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:31.700
Okay, okay.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:38.780
Are you assaulting a police officer?

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:41.260
Assaulting a police officer is a felony.

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:47.800
How much is it?

00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:48.820
I'll pay for it.

00:07:50.320 --> 00:07:51.480
It's a limited edition.

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:52.610
You can't afford it.

00:07:53.200 --> 00:07:53.600
Hey.

00:07:56.600 --> 00:07:57.440
This matter

00:07:57.760 --> 00:07:59.620
has nothing to do with the police.

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:00.410
Name a price,

00:08:00.840 --> 00:08:01.700
or a condition.

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:03.560
I'll meet it if I can.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:04.760
All of you, just...

00:08:04.760 --> 00:08:05.600
It's all your fault.

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:05.960
Ah.

00:08:05.960 --> 00:08:06.840
It's all your fault.

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:09.170
Why can't you keep your hands to yourself?

00:08:09.880 --> 00:08:11.080
You said it yourself.

00:08:11.080 --> 00:08:12.480
It has nothing to do with the police.

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:13.480
Let's go, Zhai.

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:15.130
Let's go.

00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:20.810
This way.

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:25.000
Calm down.

00:08:26.200 --> 00:08:27.930
I've been watching for a while.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.800
Why do you keep dying in the beginner's village?

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:31.060
None of your business.

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:33.780
How about this.

00:08:34.159 --> 00:08:35.159
I'll play for you.

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:36.760
One level

00:08:36.960 --> 00:08:37.690
offsets 200.

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:39.100
How about that?

00:08:45.280 --> 00:08:45.720
Sure.

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:48.120
Get me to

00:08:49.840 --> 00:08:50.840
level 30 tonight.

00:08:51.160 --> 00:08:51.520
Yeah.

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:54.880
Deal.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.480
If you don't finish the task tonight,

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:06.610
I'll file a complaint with the police tomorrow morning.

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:43.960
Hey.

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:45.440
Hey.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:49.780
What level are you?

00:09:50.760 --> 00:09:51.760
See for yourself.

00:10:01.080 --> 00:10:01.840
Wow.

00:10:03.280 --> 00:10:06.010
I really didn't expect you to be so good at gaming.

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:07.460
I'm impressed.

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:09.810
What's the use of looking impressive now?

00:10:10.280 --> 00:10:12.080
I died several times last night.

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:13.100
That's normal.

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:16.760
Dying in a game is normal,

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:19.240
but in real life,

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:20.720
you and I

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:22.740
only have one life.

00:10:25.280 --> 00:10:26.210
What do you mean?

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:40.960
Let's go.

00:10:41.560 --> 00:10:42.920
Follow me.

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:44.720
Heal me.

00:10:52.560 --> 00:10:52.920
Wait.

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:54.120
Madam.

00:10:55.080 --> 00:10:56.160
Those two policemen left.

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:56.760
They left.

00:10:58.600 --> 00:10:59.440
What are you holding?

00:10:59.440 --> 00:10:59.840
Fruit.

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:03.850
Why bring such spoiled ones to Sir?

00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:06.320
Sir said his food and drinks

00:11:06.680 --> 00:11:08.080
We have to taste it first,

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:09.960
or we'll all get fired.

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:12.400
Acting like crazy every day.

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:13.010
Go ahead.

00:11:18.040 --> 00:11:19.000
Need some vinegar.

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:19.330
Yeah.

00:11:20.760 --> 00:11:21.090
Here.

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:25.050
Can't you pour it for me?

00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:27.930
You have no sense at all.

00:11:30.520 --> 00:11:31.920
You're still reading it?

00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:33.760
If you keep reading,

00:11:33.760 --> 00:11:35.960
you'll be able to memorize this script.

00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:37.520
If I could memorize it,

00:11:37.520 --> 00:11:38.800
I would be a director.

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:42.640
Then what do you think we should act out?

00:11:45.720 --> 00:11:46.650
Hello, go ahead.

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:47.280
Captain Gu,

00:11:47.280 --> 00:11:48.740
Xu Xing has been murdered.

00:11:52.280 --> 00:11:52.720
Got it.

00:11:53.520 --> 00:11:53.850
Yeah.

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:56.200
Xu Xing was murdered.

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:26.920
Ms. Wang.

00:12:28.680 --> 00:12:29.880
Your husband is dead.

00:12:30.640 --> 00:12:32.640
Don't you have anything to say to me?

00:12:34.080 --> 00:12:35.200
Officer Gu,

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:36.720
what do you want me to say?

00:12:37.400 --> 00:12:38.280
Who do you think

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:41.460
could have killed him?

00:12:42.920 --> 00:12:43.960
If I knew,

00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:45.960
would I need you to investigate?

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:48.290
Please find the killer as soon as possible

00:12:48.400 --> 00:12:49.960
and give my family an answer.

00:12:49.960 --> 00:12:50.420
Master.

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:53.000
I asked the nanny.

00:12:53.400 --> 00:12:56.000
When she was bringing the cut fruit to the room,

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:57.130
Wang Min stopped her

00:12:57.240 --> 00:12:57.840
and

00:12:57.840 --> 00:12:58.570
scolded her.

00:12:59.640 --> 00:13:01.040
The fruit should be fine.

00:13:20.960 --> 00:13:21.690
I'm leaving.

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:22.810
Okay.

00:13:26.040 --> 00:13:27.170
This boat ticket...

00:13:27.800 --> 00:13:28.860
I booked it for you.

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.170
What do you mean?

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:35.380
It's a special situation now.

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:37.640
You... you go hide first.

00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:39.880
Come back when things blow over.

00:13:39.960 --> 00:13:40.480
No.

00:13:41.080 --> 00:13:42.320
We killed him together.

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:43.520
You must come with me.

00:13:43.560 --> 00:13:45.360
Otherwise, you'll be in danger.

00:13:45.440 --> 00:13:46.680
You killed him.